32
00:03:04,025 --> 00:03:04,745
Just a moment.

33
00:03:05,025 --> 00:03:05,704
What's wrong?

34
00:03:05,824 --> 00:03:06,544
Just a moment.

35
00:03:10,584 --> 00:03:11,785
