ظآزIn memories, the breeze is softظآز

44
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:38,250
ظآزYour smile is shimmering like starsظآز

45
00:03:38,250 --> 00:03:43,666
ظآزLighting up my lonely cornerظآز

46
00:03:44,886 --> 00:03:51,336
ظآزLove's time machine,
