ظآزThrough centuries, just to meet youظآز

49
00:04:00,454 --> 00:04:08,455
ظآزLove's time machine keeps on turningظآز

50
00:04:08,455 --> 00:04:12,808
ظآزStreaking across the skyظآز

51
00:04:13,704 --> 00:04:22,600
ظآزJust to hold youظآز

52
00:04:32,168 --> 00:04:36,136
ظآزOld times, pass slowlyظآز

53
00:04:36,136 --> 00:04:39,904
ظآزIn memories, the breeze is softظآز

54
