Try it.

55
00:04:41,264 --> 00:04:42,024
I made it myself.

56
00:04:43,784 --> 00:04:44,584
This has gone cold.

57
00:04:45,185 --> 00:04:45,945
Careful, it's hot.

58
00:04:51,985 --> 00:04:52,745
Careful, it's hot.

59
00:04:54,264 --> 00:04:54,865
How is it?

60
00:04:57,665 --> 00:04:58,185
Delicious?

61
