213
00:16:21,025 --> 00:16:21,584
Who?

214
00:16:22,265 --> 00:16:24,344
Mr. Gao Haiming. Haven't you met him?

215
00:16:27,065 --> 00:16:28,065
Mr. Gao?

216
00:16:28,305 --> 00:16:29,305
I've never heard of

217
00:16:29,305 --> 00:16:30,504
