241
00:17:32,264 --> 00:17:34,825
Sir, go to North Boyang Road first.

242
00:17:34,825 --> 00:17:35,264
Okay.

243
00:17:43,185 --> 00:17:43,825
Excuse me.

244
00:17:44,224 --> 00:17:45,865
